     26          /*******************************************************************************
     27          * Function Name  : XTI_Init
     28          * Description    : This routine is used to initialize the XTI cell:
     29          *                   -All Wake-Up Lines are disabled
     30          *                   -Interrupt disabled
     31          *                   -Walk-up mode disabled
     32          *                   -Set on the falling edge of the input wake-up line
     33          *                   -All pending bits are cleared
     34          * Input          : None.
     35          * Output         : None.
     36          * Return         : None.
     37          *******************************************************************************/

   \                                 In section .text, align 4, keep-with-next
     38          void XTI_Init (void)
     39          {
     40            XTI->SR = 0x00;
   \                     XTI_Init:
