     58          *                    XTI_WakeUp, XTI_Interrupt or XTI_WakeUpInterrupt.
     59          *                  - NewState: used to enable or disable the selected mode.
     60          *                    it can be: ENABLE or DISABLE.
     61          * Output         : None.
     62          * Return         : None.
     63          *******************************************************************************/

